{"id": "ChIJPZtDooS7woARUZWUualz_34", "rating": 5, "userRatingCount": 41, "displayName": {"text": "Sudachi Japanese restaurant", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJPZtDooS7woARUZWUualz_34/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OMllVdFJTME5FYUdKS1VVOUZaMHhtVTFoUU9VRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Very very good. They have a big traditional Japanese menu but everything is well done, high quality, fresh, and refined. Interior is very clean, comfortable, and inviting. Service is attentive and lovely. The omakase was great and I left super stuffed. No notes!\n\n2.5 hours passed by quickly!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very very good. They have a big traditional Japanese menu but everything is well done, high quality, fresh, and refined. Interior is very clean, comfortable, and inviting. Service is attentive and lovely. The omakase was great and I left super stuffed. No notes!\n\n2.5 hours passed by quickly!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Miriam Yong", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104711196562312081818/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYKqdE3Je6I3IqorCdQFYMrxFpHsuqvp2DFQYTQPGipDmbAuE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-31T17:17:24.937607510Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OMllVdFJTME5FYUdKS1VVOUZaMHhtVTFoUU9VRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OMllVdFJTME5FYUdKS1VVOUZaMHhtVTFoUU9VRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb84a2439b3d:0x7eff73a9b9949551"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPZtDooS7woARUZWUualz_34/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxNGJHSTVabTh5Ym5SUU4wdGZTVVl0TjBjeFVYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It was a very pleasant family dinner. We enjoyed chatting and relaxing in the private room. The food was delicious, and the dining environment was very clean. Although it was busy since it had just opened, the food was served at a normal pace. I recommend this restaurant and will come again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It was a very pleasant family dinner. We enjoyed chatting and relaxing in the private room. The food was delicious, and the dining environment was very clean. Although it was busy since it had just opened, the food was served at a normal pace. I recommend this restaurant and will come again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "LUCIA LIN", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107745421059594264506/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUucHfAI52Qk7KiRgvuDhQLgf5X4ReZrTxsOmDsuHEflQgmVw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-16T16:52:22.228820787Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxNGJHSTVabTh5Ym5SUU4wdGZTVVl0TjBjeFVYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxNGJHSTVabTh5Ym5SUU4wdGZTVVl0TjBjeFVYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb84a2439b3d:0x7eff73a9b9949551"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPZtDooS7woARUZWUualz_34/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1dmVtdFFkbDlvUldGV1pucHJMVUl3TjJWRFJWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "An Unforgettable Omakase Journey — A Hidden Gem You Must Experience\nFrom the moment you step through the door, it’s clear this place is something special. The interior is stunning — fresh, modern, and spotlessly clean, creating an atmosphere that instantly transports you to the heart of Japan. Every detail has been thoughtfully designed to set the perfect stage for an extraordinary dining experience.\nThe staff are nothing short of exceptional. Warm, attentive, and genuinely passionate about hospitality, they make every guest feel like a valued friend rather than just a customer. Service here flows effortlessly, adding to the overall sense of elegance.\nAnd then comes the food — and this is where the magic truly happens. Every dish is a masterpiece, bursting with authentic Japanese flavors that are rich, refined, and deeply satisfying. The quality is outstanding, and yet the pricing remains surprisingly reasonable, making this a rare find that offers true value without compromise.\nChef Haya is an absolute artist. His skill, precision, and dedication shine through in every single bite. Watching him work is a pleasure in itself — you can feel the passion and expertise poured into each carefully crafted dish.\nIf you’ve ever longed for a genuine omakase experience without traveling to Japan, this is it. The atmosphere, the flavors, the service — everything comes together to create something truly memorable.\nI loved every single moment of this meal and will absolutely be returning. This is one restaurant I will recommend to everyone, without hesitation.\nHighly, highly recommended. Don’t miss it! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "An Unforgettable Omakase Journey — A Hidden Gem You Must Experience\nFrom the moment you step through the door, it’s clear this place is something special. The interior is stunning — fresh, modern, and spotlessly clean, creating an atmosphere that instantly transports you to the heart of Japan. Every detail has been thoughtfully designed to set the perfect stage for an extraordinary dining experience.\nThe staff are nothing short of exceptional. Warm, attentive, and genuinely passionate about hospitality, they make every guest feel like a valued friend rather than just a customer. Service here flows effortlessly, adding to the overall sense of elegance.\nAnd then comes the food — and this is where the magic truly happens. Every dish is a masterpiece, bursting with authentic Japanese flavors that are rich, refined, and deeply satisfying. The quality is outstanding, and yet the pricing remains surprisingly reasonable, making this a rare find that offers true value without compromise.\nChef Haya is an absolute artist. His skill, precision, and dedication shine through in every single bite. Watching him work is a pleasure in itself — you can feel the passion and expertise poured into each carefully crafted dish.\nIf you’ve ever longed for a genuine omakase experience without traveling to Japan, this is it. The atmosphere, the flavors, the service — everything comes together to create something truly memorable.\nI loved every single moment of this meal and will absolutely be returning. This is one restaurant I will recommend to everyone, without hesitation.\nHighly, highly recommended. Don’t miss it! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tammy Pantrakul", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109430558226587330817/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqHbOcrN_CJ3FpBhvcAYrsKIvlJnKutj2a0nZlv8v0j2BKvQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-26T14:38:48.888046421Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1dmVtdFFkbDlvUldGV1pucHJMVUl3TjJWRFJWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1dmVtdFFkbDlvUldGV1pucHJMVUl3TjJWRFJWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb84a2439b3d:0x7eff73a9b9949551"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPZtDooS7woARUZWUualz_34/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaU1JuWkJhV2ROVmxkb09HMUNUa1UwWlhsWlVFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great food and great service. Everything was super fresh and authentic. Chef Haya was friendly, and the staff took great care of us.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great food and great service. Everything was super fresh and authentic. Chef Haya was friendly, and the staff took great care of us.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Frey Mau", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107143959539254784249/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2SHwMPoqf1n9FTcF6beDTn5OXH2PhCrGtshc5OiEaG6pgRQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-13T21:50:28.170912611Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaU1JuWkJhV2ROVmxkb09HMUNUa1UwWlhsWlVFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaU1JuWkJhV2ROVmxkb09HMUNUa1UwWlhsWlVFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bb84a2439b3d:0x7eff73a9b9949551"}, {"name": "places/ChIJPZtDooS7woARUZWUualz_34/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WWWNteEhUM2xQUzBKbFZtRlNURFJ4TkZsTlMwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "From appetizers to dessert, every course is thoughtfully balanced and executed at a high level. The sashimi is truly top-notch—fresh, delicate, and expertly prepared. The atmosphere is warm and welcoming, with genuinely friendly service that makes the experience even more enjoyable.\nIf you’re looking for a memorable omakase sashimi dinner, I highly recommend this place.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "From appetizers to dessert, every course is thoughtfully balanced and executed at a high level. The sashimi is truly top-notch—fresh, delicate, and expertly prepared. The atmosphere is warm and welcoming, with genuinely friendly service that makes the experience even more enjoyable.\nIf you’re looking for a memorable omakase sashimi dinner, I highly recommend this place.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Dongwook Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116735541367896259054/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiChJYDRxqwWjMb_UC1q-a4pE6YXHytbPJaQkD1Q8MaKE_LtQ7=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-20T06:46:31.463338424Z", "flag